data.Name: King Zo, Platinum Bey, Hayden, MG SAVVII
data.Description: Coming from a small town outside of Denver Colorado, King Zo (Zo Wilburn) is a determined rapper trying to let his voice be heard through his music. Zo makes it a point to connect with his audience on a larger scale. His music is a way to reflect on his life and give perspective to those who can relate or those who are searching for inspiration. Through hardship and adversity, Zo is destined to achieve his goal of being heard by millions.
